# Raw ontology dumps are large (MONDO ~53 MB, DOID ~7 MB) and re-downloadable, so
# they are not version-controlled. The compact *.index.tsv files distilled from
# them (below) ARE committed — they are what app/predict_service reads.
raw/

# Any user-supplied licensed vocabularies (SNOMED CT, OMOP/Athena, OMIM, UMLS)
# dropped here to extend predictions must not be committed (redistribution is
# license-restricted). Keep them out; commit only indexes you are permitted to.
snomed/
omop/
umls/
*.zip
